Hey guys! This code was made to analyze DNA nucleotide sequence. 
You can upload your codons and nucleotids to the Input.txt file and check if they have next mutations:

1. GAC
2. TAG
3. TGA

How to understand?
GAC:GAC (Aspartic acid): may cause sickle cell anemia if replacing another amino acid
TAG: may be a premature stop codon. It means that protein is incomplete. Associated with cancer, cystic fibrosis
TGA: may be a premature stop codon. Associated with Duchenne muscular dystrophy

Always happy to help
